title: Parisian Life Style Private Photo Shoot at Eiffel Tower
description:
Visiting Paris? 

Time to live the dream! 

Walk around the city with a local professional photographer and take home the best images of your amazing trip. In a 100% Parisian life style photo shooting, get to know Paris' highlights and secrets and keep your memories forever. 
 • 1h photo shooting with local professional photographer 
 • 50-80 high resolution EDITED photos sent by mail after the shooting 
 • groups up to ten people! 
 • Ideal for celebrating your honeymoon, engagement photos, bachelor party, family trip, birthdays and more 
 • props included for kids 
 • kids friendly activity 
 • fun, local and 100% passionate photographers!

NOTE: you will be booked in the first available hour. You will receive an email about your tour hour, meeting point and recognizing your photographer within 7 days of booking. Please check your spam and contact with us if you have not received it.

inclusions.otherDescription: 50 to 80 medium resolution EDITED photographies for online sharing
local professional photographer (English, Spanish, French, Italian)

additionalInfo.description: Suitable for all physical fitness levels
Children must be accompanied by an adult

cancellationPolicy.description: For a full refund, cancel at least 24 hours before the scheduled departure time.

itineraryItems.description:
Eiffel Tower Petit Photo Tour

In this 1h hour photo shooting in Paris, you will get the best photos with the Eiffel Tower. 

Let our photographer guide you through poses, activities and the perfect spots for the photos you have always dreamed about. 

 We will meet with the magnificent view from the Trocadero square. This is the most famous spot for photographing the city of lights and has been filmed in many publicities. Now you are the star! For better photos, let's meet early in the morning before visitors come. 

 After great shoots with the Eiffel tower, we will walk to the gardens and fountains. A great way to get original, different and very beautiful images. 

Hour: You will be booked in the earliest possible hour unless you send us a message with specific demands.

Information: AFTER BOOKING YOU WILL GET AN EMAIL THROUGH YOUR BOOKING PLATFORM. Check your spam if you do not receive it.

Important: Trocadero is one of the most popular places in Paris and it has a lot of visitors. For better choosing the time of shooting, know that the earlier we come, the better it will be. During week days in autumn and winter, it is possible to change the hour of your shooting to later on the day but it is not recommended in weekends or spring-summer.
